        <h2 class="section-title">PI Marketing Is Expensive. Bad PI Marketing Is Devastating.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cost Per Lead Is Climbing</h3>
          <p>
            Google Ads CPC for PI keywords runs $181 to $400+. In metros, truck accident
            terms hit $1,000 per click. Without a strategy, you are buying clicks that never convert.
          </p>
          <span class="pain-stat">$442 average CPL on Google Ads</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Intake Leaks Kill ROI</h3>
          <p>
            Firms that respond to leads within 5 minutes see 400% higher conversion rates.
            Most PI firms take hours. Every slow response is a signed case going to your competitor.
          </p>
          <span class="pain-stat">400% conversion lift from 5-min response</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m15 9-6 6M9 9l6 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>No Channel Attribution</h3>
          <p>
            You run Google Ads, SEO, LSAs, and maybe TV. You cannot tell which channel
            produced your last 10 signed cases. Without attribution, every dollar is a guess.
          </p>
          <span class="pain-stat">60% of PI budgets wasted without tracking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Agencies Without Accountability</h3>
          <p>
            Your SEO agency shows you rankings. Your PPC agency shows you clicks.
            Nobody shows you cost per signed case. Nobody owns the full picture.
          </p>
          <span class="pain-stat">82% report poor paid search ROI</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benchmarks Section -->
  <section class="benchmarks-section">
