      <div class="benchmarks-grid">
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">Google Ads CPL</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">$442</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">5-15% conversion to signed case</span>
        </div>
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">SEO CPL</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">$183</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">15-20% conversion to signed case</span>
        </div>
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">LSA CPL</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">$378</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">Local high-intent searches</span>
        </div>
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">Referral CPL</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">&lt;$100</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">15-20%+ conversion rate</span>
        </div>
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">Cost Per Signed Case</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">$1,500-$2,500</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">Exclusive leads (owned channels)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="benchmark-card">
          <span class="benchmark-label">Shared Lead Cost</span>
          <span class="benchmark-value">$3,000-$6,000</span>
          <span class="benchmark-detail">2-5% conversion rate</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="benchmarks-cta">
        <a href="/insights/pi-cost-per-lead-benchmarks/" class="btn btn-outline-white">
          See Full Benchmark Report â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do Section -->
  <section class="solution-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-badge-light">What a Fractional CMO Does for PI</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">We Own the Strategy. We Fix the System.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-grid">
        <div class="solution-card featured">
          <span class="solution-number">01</span>
          <h3>Channel-Level Attribution</h3>
          <p>
            We track every lead from first click to signed retainer. You will know
            exactly what each channel costs per signed case, not per lead.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <span class="solution-number">02</span>
          <h3>Budget Reallocation</h3>
          <p>
            Most PI firms over-invest in Google Ads and under-invest in SEO.
            We shift spend toward channels with better cost per signed case ratios.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <span class="solution-number">03</span>
          <h3>Intake Optimization</h3>
          <p>
            Speed to lead. Call tracking. Intake scripts. CRM workflows.
            We close the gap between "lead" and "signed case" where most firms lose 40% of potential clients.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <span class="solution-number">04</span>
          <h3>Vendor Accountability</h3>
          <p>
            We manage your SEO agency, your PPC team, your web developer.
            Every vendor reports on metrics that matter: signed cases, not vanity numbers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <span class="solution-number">05</span>
          <h3>SEO and Content Strategy</h3>
          <p>
            SEO delivers leads at $183 CPL with 15-20% conversion. We build the content
            strategy, keyword targets, and local SEO foundation that compounds over time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <span class="solution-number">06</span>
          <h3>Monthly Reporting You Actually Read</h3>
          <p>
            One dashboard. Cost per signed case by channel. Lead volume trends.
            Intake conversion rates. No 40-page reports full of vanity metrics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results Section -->
  <section class="results-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-badge">Results</span>
        <h2 class="section-title-light">What the Data Shows</h2>
      </div>
