          <span class="result-number">40%</span>
          <span class="result-label">Reduction in client acquisition costs</span>
          <span class="result-source">Through full-funnel optimization</span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <span class="result-number">31%</span>
          <span class="result-label">Year-over-year caseload increase</span>
          <span class="result-source">PI firm with fractional CMO engagement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card">
          <span class="result-number">92%</span>
          <span class="result-label">Client retention rate over 2+ years</span>
          <span class="result-source">Because measurable results keep clients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-badge-light">FAQ</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions from PI Firm Owners</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">How much does a fractional CMO cost for a PI firm?</summary>
          <p class="faq-answer">
            A fractional CMO costs about 70% less than a full-time hire. Full-time CMOs
            run $300K+ annually in salary, benefits, and equity. Fractional engagements
            for PI firms typically run $8K to $15K monthly for senior-level marketing
            leadership, strategy, vendor management, and accountability.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">What results can a PI firm expect?</summary>
          <p class="faq-answer">
            Industry data shows law firms with fractional CMOs grow 3x faster than firms
            without marketing leadership. PI firms typically see 40% lower client acquisition
            costs and 2 to 3x growth in signed cases within 9 months. Quick wins from intake
            optimization and channel reallocation usually appear within 90 days.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">How is this different from hiring a marketing agency?</summary>
          <p class="faq-answer">
            An agency executes tactics. A fractional CMO owns the strategy. We sit in your
            leadership meetings, manage your vendors, track cost per signed case by channel,
            and make budget decisions based on data. We are accountable for revenue growth,
            not activity metrics like impressions or clicks.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">How long until we see results?</summary>
          <p class="faq-answer">
            Quick wins appear within 90 days through intake optimization and paid channel
            restructuring. Significant revenue impact (300% ROI) typically materializes
            within 18 to 24 months as SEO, content, and referral channels compound.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">Do you replace our current marketing vendors?</summary>
          <p class="faq-answer">
            Not necessarily. We evaluate your current vendors against performance benchmarks.
            Good vendors stay. Underperformers get replaced with vetted partners from our network.
            We manage the entire vendor ecosystem so you do not have to.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Stop Guessing. Start Measuring.</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">
          We will audit your current PI marketing, benchmark your cost per signed case
          by channel, and tell you exactly where to cut waste. No commitment required.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">
          Get a Free Marketing Audit
        </a>
        <p class="cta-disclaimer">
          No contracts. No pressure. Just data.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

